## 5ct Lab Grown Cushion Cut Diamond Ring

The lab 5ct cushion ring at $10,157 IGI D-VVS1 is the most dramatic price-to-presence ratio in the diamond market: 11mm face-up, top colour, clean clarity, and a total ring cost under $12,000. At 5ct, the lab advantage is absolute.

